title: [COMPLETE] OCE Platform Maintenance - 2016-10-26 @ 0600 AEDT
body:
Hi Folks

We'll be doing some planned maintenance on the OCE servers tomorrow morning (Wednesday 26th October)

* Ranked Queues will be disabled at 0430 am AEDT (Sydney Time)
* The servers will be shut down at 0600 AEDT for a 3 hour maintenance window, opening back up at 0900 AEDT.

I'll post here if there are any updates to the plan.

Cheers!
Mindstar

replies.body: did this create an issue with spectating at all? i havent been able to spec any matches since i logged on today, wont let me connect.

Is this to fix the club issue?
that and general maintenance.

Hi

This was a separate system being worked on - not related to clubs.  That one is still in progress :)

Cheers
Mindstar
